und opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "cell-switch-feature-announcement"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"secondary-group\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#secondary-group\" class=\"peer\">Secondary Group</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "cell-switch-secondary-group"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"settings-group\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#settings-group\" class=\"peer\">Settings Group</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "cell-switch-settings-group"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"variants\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#variants\" class=\"peer\">Variants</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "cell-switch-variants"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"css-classes\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#css-classes\" class=\"peer\">CSS Classes</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"base-classes\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#base-classes\" class=\"peer\">Base Classes</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>.cell-switch</code> - Root wrapper (renders as a <code>label</code> via HeroUI Switch)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"element-classes\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#element-classes\" class=\"peer\">Element Classes</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>.cell-switch__trigger</code> - The visible cell row container</li>\n<li><code>.cell-switch__trigger--default</code> - Default variant trigger styling</li>\n<li><code>.cell-switch__trigger--secondary</code> - Secondary variant trigger styling</li>\n<li><code>.cell-switch__label</code> - Leading text label</li>\n<li><code>.cell-switch__control</code> - Switch control wrapper</li>\n<li><code>.cell-switch__control--secondary</code> - Secondary variant control styling</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"variant-classes\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#variant-classes\" class=\"peer\">Variant Classes</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>.cell-switch--secondary</code> - Secondary variant on the root</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"api-reference\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#api-reference\" class=\"peer\">API Reference</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"cellswitch\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#cellswitch\" class=\"peer\">CellSwitch</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>The root component. Wraps HeroUI <a href=\"https://heroui.com/docs/react/components/switch\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Switch</a> with cell-style layout. Clicking anywhere in the cell toggles the switch.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>variant</code></td><td><code>'default' | 'secondary'</code></td><td><code>'default'</code></td><td>Visual style variant</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all <a href=\"https://heroui.com/docs/react/components/switch\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">HeroUI Switch</a> props except <code>variant</code>.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"cellswitchtrigger\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#cellswitchtrigger\" class=\"peer\">CellSwitch.Trigger</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>The visible cell row containing the label and switch control.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>Label and control elements</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>div</code> HTML attributes.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"cellswitchlabel\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#cellswitchlabel\" class=\"peer\">CellSwitch.Label</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Leading text label rendered as a <code>span</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>Label text</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>span</code> HTML attributes.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"cellswitchcontrol\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#cellswitchcontrol\" class=\"peer\">CellSwitch.Control</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Switch control. Renders the default HeroUI <code>Switch.Thumb</code> when no children are provided.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>Custom control content</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all HeroUI <code>Switch.Control</code> props.</p></div><div class=\"@container my-8 grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-fd-accent-foreground hover:bg-surface-secondary @max-lg:col-span-full flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl p-4 text-sm transition-none\" href=\"/docs/react/components/cell-slider\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"-mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M10.53 2.97a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06L6.56 8l3.97 3.97a.75.75 0 1 1-1.06 1.06l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06l4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg><p>Cell Slider</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">A range slider styled as a settings cell with label, value display, and step configuration.</p></a><a class=\"hover:text-fd-accent-foreground hover:bg-surface-secondary @max-lg:col-span-full flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl p-4 text-sm transition-none text-end\" href=\"/docs/react/components/checkbox-button-group\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"-mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5.47 13.03a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06L9.44 8 5.47 4.03a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l4.5 4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-4.5 4.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg><p>Checkbox Button Group</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">A multi-selection button group with card-style checkboxes, icons, and custom indicators.</p></a></div>"}], "tocHtml": "<a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#usage\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Usage</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#anatomy\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Anatomy</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#controlled\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Controlled</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#disabled\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Disabled</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#feature-announcement\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Feature Announcement</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#secondary-group\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Secondary Group</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#settings-group\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Settings Group</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#variants\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Variants</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#css-classes\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">CSS Classes</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#base-classes\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Base Classes</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#element-classes\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Element Classes</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#variant-classes\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Variant Classes</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#api-reference\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">API Reference</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#cellswitch\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">CellSwitch</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#cellswitchtrigger\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">CellSwitch.Trigger</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#cellswitchlabel\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">CellSwitch.Label</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#cellswitchcontrol\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">CellSwitch.Control</a>"}